{
  "$schema": "https://github.com/SettingDust/ModSets/raw/main/rules.schema.json",
  "text": {"text":"Common","bold":true,"color":"#76deea"},
  "description": "The sets you may want to toggle.\n\nRemember, they all require the game to restart.",
  "rules": [
    {
      "text": "üìñ EMI Recipe Viewer",
      "description": ["The ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"recipe viewer"}," and anything that has to do with it.\n\nDisable if another recipe viewer is desired.\n",{"color":"dark_gray","text":"Fun fact: EMI doesn't stand for anything, really."}],
      "controller": {
        "type": "boolean",
        "id": "emi_set"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "üé§ Voice Chat",
      "description": ["",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Simple Voice Chat"}," and other mods that depend on it.\n\nIf disabled, other players will know through an ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"icon"}," next to the nickname."],
      "controller": {
        "type": "boolean",
        "id": "voice_chat_set"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "üßª CraftPresence",
      "description": ["Shares the modpack's activity on ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Discord"},".\n\n",{"color":"dark_gray","text":"It's okay, ","extra":[{"italic":true,"text":"we can mind our business..."}]}],
      "controller": {
        "type": "boolean",
        "id": "craftpresence"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {"text": "Performance Desperation", "color": "#55a6e4", "bold": true},
      "description": ["",{"color":"white","text":"I believe "},{"color":"#0076b4","bold":true,"underlined":true,"text":"@SueTheMimiga","clickEvent":{"action":"open_url","value":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/E16spB6XEAU5jCH.jpg"}},{"color":"white","text":" is going to enjoy this üëÄ"}],
      "controller": {
        "type": "rules_group",
        "collapsed": false,
        "rules": [
          {
            "text": "üîä Realistic Sounds",
            "description": ["Makes most ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"sounds"}," reverb, echo, and bounce across rooms in an exceedingly, ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"physically-accurate "},"fashion.\n\nThis has a huge performance impact. Disable if you believe the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"CPU"}," is struggling.\nThese features can also be customized in the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Mods\u00A0>\u00A0Sound\u00A0Physics\u00A0Reloaded"}," menu, but they are ",{"color":"red","text":"reset"}," every Bubble Cobble update."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "realistic_sound_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üîâ Sounds",
            "description": ["Plays ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"sounds"}," for many more occasions, such as grabbing ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"items"}," and opening ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"menus"},", as well as adding unique ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"block sounds"},".\n\nDisable if the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"CPU"}," is struggling.\nThese features can also be customized in the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Mods\u00A0>\u00A0Sounds"}, " menu."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "sound_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "‚ú® Particles",
            "description": ["Cosmetic, mostly ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"particle"},"-enhancing mods. Moodier ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"rain"},", inventory interactions, and ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"arrow trails"}," included.\n\nDisable if you believe the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"GPU"}," cannot keep up."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "particle_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üå´ Fog",
            "description": ["Enhances Minecraft's fog to be thicker and more dynamic.\n\nDisable if you believe the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"GPU"}," cannot keep up.\nRemember, it can be toggled in-game by pressing ",{"color":"aqua","keybind":"key.fog.toggle"},".\nThese features can also be customized in the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Mods\u00A0>\u00A0Fog"}," menu."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "fog"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üî• Shaders",
            "description": ["",{"color":"blue","text":"Iris","clickEvent":{"action":"open_url","value":"https://www.irisshaders.dev/"}},", the mod that can make everything look like ",{"color":"#fafcff","text":"t"},{"color":"#f6f8fe","text":"h"},{"color":"#f1f5fe","text":"e"},{"color":"#ecf2fe","text":"y "},{"color":"#e3ebfd","text":"h"},{"color":"#dfe8fd","text":"i"},{"color":"#dae5fd","text":"r"},{"color":"#d5e2fd","text":"e"},{"color":"#d1defc","text":"d "},{"color":"#c7d8fc","text":"t"},{"color":"#c3d5fc","text":"h"},{"color":"#bed1fb","text":"a"},{"color":"#bacefb","text":"t "},{"color":"#b0c8fb","text":"m"},{"color":"#acc4fa","text":"a"},{"color":"#a7c1fa","text":"n"},".\n\nTo be honest, even if enabled, it doesn't have ",{"italic":true,"text":"much"}," of an impact on its own. Shaders, on the other hand...\nRemember, shaders can be accessed by pressing ",{"color":"aqua","keybind":"iris.keybind.shaderPackSelection"}," and toggled by pressing ",{"color":"aqua","keybind":"iris.keybind.toggleShaders"},"."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "shader_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üíÉ Animation",
            "description": ["Enhances ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"player animations "},"on several occasions. From showing players holding ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Torches"}," upwards, to rummaging their ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Inventory"},".\n\nDisable if you believe the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"CPU"}," and ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"GPU"}," cannot keep up."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "animation_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üñº Retextures",
            "description": ["Retextures ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Potions"}," and ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Enchanted Books"}," to appear more distinct.\n\nDisable if you believe the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"GPU"}," cannot keep up, although it mostly makes a difference on start-up."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "enchanted_retexture_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üó∫ Map",
            "description": ["",{"color":"blue","text":"Xaero's Map","clickEvent":{"action":"open_url","value":"https://modrinth.com/mod/xaeros-world-map"}},", Minimap, and anything to do with it.\n\nDisable if the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"CPU"}," cannot keep up, although I ",{"italic":true,"text":"seriously"}," doubt you'd want to."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "xaero_map_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üî¶ Dynamic Lights",
            "description": ["",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Illuminates"}," the surroundings in many occasions, such as when holding ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Torches"},".\n\nDisable if the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"CPU"}," cannot keep up.\nRemember, the lighting's quality can be changed in the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Video Settings"}," without needing to disable the mod."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "fabric_renderer_api_v1"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "üåÅ Chunks Fade in",
            "description": ["Makes ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"loaded chunks"}," fade-in ",{"italic":true,"text":"","extra":[{"color":"#f4f7fe","text":"s"},{"color":"#e9f0fe","text":"m"},{"color":"#dee8fd","text":"o"},{"color":"#d3e0fd","text":"o"},{"color":"#c8d8fc","text":"t"},{"color":"#bdd1fb","text":"h"},{"color":"#b2c9fb","text":"l"},{"color":"#a7c1fa","text":"y"}]},".\n\nDisable if the ",{"color":"dark_aqua","text":"GPU"}," cannot keep up, although I doubt it.\nRemember, the effect can be customized in the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"Video Settings"}," without needing to disable the mod."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "chunksfadein"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {"text": "‚ö† Server-side ‚ö†", "color": "red", "bold": true},
      "description": ["These mods are mostly, practically needed on the ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"server"},".\n\nDisable to potentially load the game faster, especially in singleplayer worlds, at the cost of a ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"completely different"}," modpack experience."],
      "controller": {
        "type": "rules_group",
        "collapsed": true,
        "rules": [
          {
            "text": "Vanilla-like Structures",
            "description": ["Adds many new ",{"color":"#76deea","text":"structures"}," that do not rely on other mods to function."],
            "controller": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "id": "server_structures_set"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Miscellaneous",
            "description": "Server-only mods I don't feel like explaining and/or categorizing.",
            "controller": {
              "type": "mods_group",
              "collapsed": "true",
              "ids": [
                "chunky",
                "firespreadtweaks",
                "sparsestructures",
                "temperaturebands",
                "mendingrework",
                "neruina"
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}